Re-scan recent mail for deliveries

Usage: mxr deliveries scan [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --since-days <SINCE_DAYS>  Window in days to scan (default 90)
      --dry-run                  Preview detections without writing or calling the LLM
  -h, --help                     Print help
